Pop-up za shopping cart, lista od selektirani produkti

Home so card da se napravat reklamite


ROLES: BUYERS AND SELLERS

Buyers(moze da se iskoriste user model)
    -Home page with ads of all services,
    -Shopping cart service


Sellers
    -Can add ads on home page
        -Ads can be products or services (forms)
        -If ad i a service, you can call or select date and time on the site
    -Maps
    -You can open sellers account and see all ads from the seller
        -Account has picture, description and you can leave rating

Ads(Moze da se iskoriste Product model)
    -Can be edited
    -Cards with desc, basic info and link to seller,
    -button to add to cart

